        "text": "### Stability Constants Reported\n\nAll measurements were made in **water** at **25 °C**. The study reported constants for seven distinct equilibria across two background electrolytes:\n\n| VLM ID | Species / Equilibrium | Constant Type | Value | I (mol/L) | Electrolyte |\n|--------|-----------------------|---------------|-------|-----------|-------------|\n| vlm_98907 | [ZnL]/[Zn][L] — ZnL formation | log K | **6.63** | 0.15 | NaCl |\n| vlm_98905 | [ZnL]/[Zn][L] — ZnL formation | log K | **6.51** | 0.15 | NaNO₃ |\n| vlm_98919 | [ZnL₂]/[Zn][L]² — ZnL₂ overall | log β₂ | **12.62** | 0.15 | NaCl |\n| vlm_98916 | [ZnL₂]/[Zn][L]² — ZnL₂ overall | log β₂ | **12.14** | 0.15 | NaNO₃ |\n| vlm_98924 | [ZnHL]/[ZnL][H] — protonation of ZnL | log K | **5.43** | 0.15 | NaCl |\n| vlm_98921 | [ZnHL]/[ZnL][H] — protonation of ZnL | log K | **4.89** | 0.15 | NaNO₃ |\n| vlm_98927 | [ZnHL₂]/[ZnL₂][H] — protonation of ZnL₂ | log K | **5.94** | 0.15 | NaCl |",
